<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-85-0081 </DOCNO><TEXT>This documentation contains opinions on the questions of the legal aspectsof energy and energy supply. The subjects are, in particular: Energyeconomy in the year 2000, conflicting aims in the energy economy - safeand cheap or economical supply?, status of the structural reform forelectricity tariffs, applicability of Paragraph 1 or Paragraph 18 GWBon regional protection and energy supply contracts, problems of terminationof regional protection according to Paragraph 103a - preparing the supplyof regions unknown until now and the regulation of energy economy inthe USA - inferences for German energy laws.</TEXT></DOC>